hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: The National Gallery pharmaclinix lightenex gold serum Clean lines, pale colours, elegant modern furniture and hardwood floors characterise the bright, airy and restful rooms of the least chalet-like hotel in town. As you'd expect from such a hotel, it also has a stylish cocktail bar and lobby with a giant sunken fireplace pit. The penthouse suites have open fires and private outdoor hot tubs with views. Doubles CHF 177.50-330.
